quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  31,1,"Alif, Lam, Mim."
  31,2,"Tsino nitsinyaali tsieshitabu shiamachesi."
  31,3,"Obulunjifu nende tsimbabaasi khubalia bakholanga amalayi."
  31,4,"Balia balumililanga okhulaama (iswala) nende bahininjia eshihanwa (izakaa), ne abali nende obusuubili obukhongo muno khuyinyanga yeyindukho."
  31,5,"Abo nibo bali khubulunjifu okhurula khu Nyasaye wabu, ne abo nibo abalibura."
  31,6,"Ne mubandu balimwo balia abakulanga amakhuwa kabula oluchendo mbu kho banyoole okhukosia khunjila ya Nyasaye nibalamanyile liosi liosi tawe, ne bakholelanga injila eyo omubayo. Abo baliba nende eshinyasio shiokhututuyia."
  31,7,"Ne nibasoomelwa tsinyaali tsiefu, batsihelesinjia emikongo mukhwilola shinga balatsiwulilekhwo tawe, shinga mumarwi kabu kalimwo iwula, kho boosilie likhuwa lia eshinyasio eshilulu."
  31,8,"Toto balia abasuubila mana nibakhola amalayi baliba nende emikunda chobwokholo mwikulu."
  31,9,"Balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsioosi. Ni indache ya Nyasaye yatoto, naye niye Owamaani, Owamachesi muno."
  31,10,"Yalonga likulu libula tsisilo tsiamulola, ne nara khwililoba tsingulu lilabatengeyiatengeyia tawe, naye yasalasiamwo tsisolo tsiabuli imbia, ne khukwisinjia amatsi okhurula hekulu, mana nikhumesiamwo emimela emilayi echia buli imbia."
  31,11,"Khuno nokhuloonga khwa Nyasaye, kho munzechesiekhwo nishina shiabaloonga balia abalali Ye (Nyasaye), halali abonooni bali mubukori bulolekha."